yang diperbuat manusia di atasnya)","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":99,"arabic":"الزّلزلة","latin":"Az-Zalzalah","transliteration":"Az-Zalzalah","translation":"Guncangan","num_ayah":8,"page":599,"location":"Madaniyah"}},{"id":6143,"surah_id":99,"ayah":5,"page":599,"quarter_hizb":60.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"بِاَنَّ رَبَّكَ اَوْحٰى لَهَاۗ","kitabah":"بِاَنَّ رَبَّكَ اَوْحٰى لَهَاۗ","latin":"Bi'anna rabbaka auḥā lahā.","arabic_words":["بِاَنَّ","رَبَّكَ","اَوْحٰى","لَهَاۗ"],"translation":"karena sesungguhnya Tuhanmu telah memerintahkan (yang demikian itu) kepadanya.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":99,"arabic":"الزّلزلة","latin":"Az-Zalzalah","transliteration":"Az-Zalzalah","translation":"Guncangan","num_ayah":8,"page":599,"location":"Madaniyah"}},{"id":6144,"surah_id":99,"ayah":6,"page":599,"quarter_hizb":60.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"يَوْمَىِٕذٍ يَّصْدُرُ النَّاسُ اَشْتَاتًا ەۙ لِّيُرَوْا اَعْمَالَهُمْۗ","kitabah":"يَوْمَىِٕذٍ يَّصْدُرُ النَّاسُ اَشْتَاتًا ەۙ لِّيُرَوْا اَعْمَالَهُمْۗ","latin":"Yauma'iżiy yaṣdurun-nāsu asytātā(n), liyurau a‘mālahum.","arabic_words":["يَوْمَىِٕذٍ","يَّصْدُرُ","النَّاسُ","اَشْتَاتًا","ەۙ","لِّيُرَوْا","اَعْمَالَهُمْۗ"],"translation":"Pada hari itu manusia keluar (dari kuburnya) dalam keadaan terpencar untuk diperlihatkan kepada mereka (balasan) semua perbuatan mereka.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":99,"arabic":"الزّلزلة","latin":"Az-Zalzalah","transliteration":"Az-Zalzalah","translation":"Guncangan","num_ayah":8,"page":599,"location":"Madaniyah"}},{"id":6145,"surah_id":99,"ayah":7,"page":599,"quarter_hizb":60.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"فَمَنْ يَّعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ خَيْرًا يَّرَهٗۚ","kitabah":"فَمَنْ يَّعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ خَيْرًا يَّرَهٗۚ","latin":"Famay ya‘mal miṡqāla żarratin khairay yarah(ū).","arabic_words":["فَمَنْ","يَّعْمَلْ","مِثْقَالَ","ذَرَّةٍ","خَيْرًا","يَّرَهٗۚ"],"translation":"Siapa yang mengerjakan kebaikan seberat zarah, dia akan melihat (balasan)-nya.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":99,"arabic":"الزّلزلة","latin":"Az-Zalzalah","transliteration":"Az-Zalzalah","translation":"Guncangan","num_ayah":8,"page":599,"location":"Madaniyah"}},{"id":6146,"surah_id":99,"ayah":8,"page":599,"quarter_hizb":60.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"وَمَنْ يَّعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ شَرًّا يَّرَهٗ ࣖ","kitabah":"وَمَنْ يَّعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ شَرًّا يَّرَهٗ ࣖ","latin":"Wa may ya‘mal miṡqāla żarratin syarray yarah(ū).","arabic_words":["وَمَنْ","يَّعْمَلْ","مِثْقَالَ","ذَرَّةٍ","شَرًّا","يَّرَهٗ ࣖ"],"translation":"Siapa yang mengerjakan kejahatan seberat zarah, dia akan melihat (balasan)-nya.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":99,"arabic":"الزّلزلة","latin":"Az-Zalzalah","transliteration":"Az-Zalzalah","translation":"Guncangan","num_ayah":8,"page":599,"location":"Madaniyah"}}]}